    <h4>This is whithout subscript:</h4>
    CH4 + O2 => H2O + CO2
    <h4>This is with subscript:</h4>
    CH<sub>4</sub> + O<sub>2</sub> => H<sub>2</sub>O + CO<sub>2</sub>

    <hr>
    <h4>This is without superscript:</h4><br>
    (a+b)2 = a2 + b2 + 2ab<br>
    <h4>This is with superscript:</h4><br>
    (a+b)<sup>2</sup> = a<sup>2</sup> + b<sup>2</sup> + 2ab


